CSS

```
 .rect {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        background-color: pink;
        position: relative;
        margin: 100px;
    }

    .rect::before,
    .rect::after {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        content: '';
        z-index: -1;
        margin: -5%;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px;
        animation: clipMe 8s linear infinite;
    }

    .rect::after {
        animation-delay: -4s;
    }

    @keyframes clipMe {
        0%,
        100% {
            clip: rect(0, 220px, 2px, 0)
        }
        25% {
            clip: rect(0, 2px, 220px, 0)
        }
        50% {
            clip: rect(218px, 220px, 220px, 0)
        }
        75% {
            clip: rect(0, 220px, 220px, 218px)
        }
    }
```

